1) Dept 30 employees sorted by salary

**Aim: To display employees in dept 30 sorted by salary descending.** \
Requirement: Employee table with deptno and salary.\
Theory: ORDER BY sorts records.\
Query: SELECT ename, job
FROM employee
WHERE deptno = 30
ORDER BY sal DESC;
