7) Total salary (salary + commission)

**Aim: To calculate total salary.** \
Requirement: Salary and commission columns.\
Theory: Arithmetic operations compute values.\
Query: SELECT empno, (sal + IFNULL(comm,0)) AS total_salary
FROM employee;
